}
<br>
<div class="card mb-3" style="max-width: 540px;">
  <div class="row g-0">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <img src="/assets/$theme$/accessible.png" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="Accessibility icon">
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Accessible</h5>
        <p class="card-text">Everyone deserves equal access to technology, and a disability/disturb shouldn't get in the way of achieving so.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<br>
<div class="card mb-3" style="max-width: 540px;">
  <div class="row g-0">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <img src="/assets/$theme$/user-first.png" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="Users First icon">
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Users First</h5>
        <p class="card-text">We work a lot on minimizing the risk of getting this website blocked for any possible reason. This is done to avoid the risk of getting this website blocked.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<br>
<div class="card mb-3" style="max-width: 540px;">
