    <div class="col-md-4">
      <img src="/assets/$theme$/curated.png" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="Curated icon">
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Well-done</h5>
        <p class="card-text">The Coderkick experience must reach perfection. It's the hardest part, it's achieved in months or even years' time, but it is possible.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<br>
<div class="card mb-3" style="max-width: 540px;">
  <div class="row g-0">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <img src="/assets/$theme$/customizable.png" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="Customizable icon">
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Yours</h5>
