    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">...and free</h5>
        <p class="card-text">We lose money every month to ensure Coderkick is free for everyone, and the amount of losses will only increase as we get more users. If you can, you might <a href="/donate">donate</a> to help us manage these costs.<i class="bi bi-heart-fill"></i></p>

